                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RuntimeStatefulSerializerFactory cannot be serialized due to a non-serializable field (&lt;tt&gt;ClassLoader loader&lt;/tt&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
